<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>Execution on ErrorCode — Error Code Reference &amp; Solutions</title><link>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/tags/execution/</link><description>Recent content in Execution on ErrorCode — Error Code Reference &amp; Solutions</description><generator>Hugo</generator><language>en</language><atom:link href="https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/tags/execution/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>[Solution] Gradle Task Execution Failed</title><link>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/tools/gradle/task-error/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/tools/gradle/task-error/</guid><description>&lt;h1 id="gradle-task-execution-failed"&gt;Gradle Task Execution Failed&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;A task execution failure means Gradle started a task but the task returned a non-zero exit code or threw an exception during its execution. The build is interrupted at that point.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id="common-causes"&gt;Common Causes&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Compilation errors in source code&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Test failures with strict test configurations&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Missing files or directories expected by the task&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Insufficient memory or system resources for the task&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2 id="how-to-fix"&gt;How to Fix&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;h3 id="run-with-stack-trace"&gt;Run with Stack Trace&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;./gradlew &amp;lt;task-name&amp;gt; --stacktrace
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h3 id="run-with-info-logging"&gt;Run with Info Logging&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;./gradlew &amp;lt;task-name&amp;gt; --info
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h3 id="skip-failing-tests-temporarily"&gt;Skip Failing Tests Temporarily&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;./gradlew build -x test
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h3 id="increase-jvm-memory"&gt;Increase JVM Memory&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# gradle.properties&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;org.gradle.jvmargs&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;-Xmx4g -XX:MaxMetaspaceSize&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;512m
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h3 id="fix-the-specific-task"&gt;Fix the Specific Task&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-groovy" data-lang="groovy"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;tasks&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;register&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#39;myTask&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;)&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;{&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; doLast &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;{&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Ensure this path exists
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; file&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#39;build/output&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;).&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;mkdirs&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;()&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;}&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;}&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 id="examples"&gt;Examples&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# Compilation failure&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;./gradlew compileJava
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# FAILURE: Build failed with an exception.&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# * What went wrong: Execution failed for task &amp;#39;:compileJava&amp;#39;.&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# Fix: correct the source code errors&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# Test failure&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;./gradlew test
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# FAILURE: Build failed with an exception.&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# * What went wrong: 3 tests failed.&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# Fix: fix failing tests or use ./gradlew build -x test&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 id="related-errors"&gt;Related Errors&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/tools/gradle/config-error4/"&gt;Configuration Error&lt;/a&gt; — build script evaluation failure&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/tools/gradle/cache-error3/"&gt;Cache Error&lt;/a&gt; — corrupted build cache&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;</description></item><item><title>[Solution] MATLAB Script Runtime Error Fix</title><link>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/matlab/script-error10/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/matlab/script-error10/</guid><description>&lt;h1 id="matlab-script-runtime-error-fix"&gt;MATLAB Script Runtime Error Fix&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This error occurs when MATLAB encounters a problem while executing a script file (&lt;code&gt;.m&lt;/code&gt;). The error message varies depending on the specific issue, but it typically includes the script name and line number where the error occurred: &lt;code&gt;Error in scriptName (line X)&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id="description"&gt;Description&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Script errors in MATLAB are not a single error code but rather a catch-all for any runtime failure that occurs during script execution. MATLAB reports the script name and line number to help locate the problem. The underlying cause could be anything from an undefined variable to an invalid operation on array elements.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>[Solution] Maven Plugin Execution Error</title><link>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/tools/maven/plugin-error2/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/tools/maven/plugin-error2/</guid><description>&lt;h1 id="maven-plugin-execution-error"&gt;Maven Plugin Execution Error&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;A plugin execution error occurs when a Maven plugin goal fails during the build lifecycle. The plugin may have invalid configuration, missing dependencies, or encounter a runtime error.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id="common-causes"&gt;Common Causes&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;The plugin version is missing or incompatible with the current Maven version&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;The plugin configuration in &lt;code&gt;pom.xml&lt;/code&gt; is incorrect&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A plugin dependency is missing from the plugin&amp;rsquo;s classpath&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;The plugin goal is not compatible with the current packaging type&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2 id="how-to-fix"&gt;How to Fix&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;h3 id="specify-plugin-version-explicitly"&gt;Specify Plugin Version Explicitly&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-xml" data-lang="xml"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;&amp;lt;plugin&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;&amp;lt;groupId&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;org.apache.maven.plugins&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;&amp;lt;/groupId&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;&amp;lt;artifactId&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;maven-surefire-plugin&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;&amp;lt;/artifactId&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;&amp;lt;version&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;3.2.5&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;&amp;lt;/version&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;&amp;lt;/plugin&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h3 id="run-with-debug-output"&gt;Run with Debug Output&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;mvn package -X
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h3 id="skip-the-failing-plugin"&gt;Skip the Failing Plugin&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;mvn package -Dmaven.test.skip&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;true
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h3 id="check-plugin-goal-compatibility"&gt;Check Plugin Goal Compatibility&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;mvn &amp;lt;plugin&amp;gt;:&amp;lt;goal&amp;gt; --help
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h3 id="fix-plugin-configuration"&gt;Fix Plugin Configuration&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-xml" data-lang="xml"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;&amp;lt;plugin&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;&amp;lt;groupId&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;org.apache.maven.plugins&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;&amp;lt;/groupId&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;&amp;lt;artifactId&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;maven-compiler-plugin&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;&amp;lt;/artifactId&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;&amp;lt;configuration&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;&amp;lt;source&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;17&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;&amp;lt;/source&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;&amp;lt;target&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;17&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;&amp;lt;/target&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;&amp;lt;/configuration&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;&amp;lt;/plugin&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 id="examples"&gt;Examples&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# Missing plugin version&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# [ERROR] Failed to execute goal on project my-app&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# Fix: add &amp;lt;version&amp;gt; to the plugin in pom.xml&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# Plugin goal incompatible with packaging&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# [ERROR] Failed to execute goal: WAR packaging requires maven-war-plugin&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# Fix: use the correct plugin for the packaging type&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 id="related-errors"&gt;Related Errors&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/tools/maven/profile-error/"&gt;Profile Error&lt;/a&gt; — profile not found&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/tools/maven/repository-error/"&gt;Repository Error&lt;/a&gt; — dependency resolution failure&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;</description></item><item><title>Runtime error</title><link>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/fortran/runtime-error11/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/fortran/runtime-error11/</guid><description>&lt;h2 id="what-this-error-means"&gt;What This Error Means&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;A runtime error is a broad category of errors that occur while the program is executing, as opposed to compile-time or link-time errors. In Fortran, runtime errors include conditions like invalid input, unhandled edge cases, resource exhaustion, and violated program assumptions. They are typically caught by the runtime system and reported with an error message and line number.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id="common-causes"&gt;Common Causes&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Invalid numeric operations (e.g., square root of a negative number)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Uninitialized variables used in computations&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Array index out of bounds (detected by runtime bounds checking)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Division by zero or overflow in arithmetic expressions&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2 id="how-to-fix"&gt;How to Fix&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-fortran" data-lang="fortran"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;! WRONG: No error handling for invalid input
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;program&lt;/span&gt; runtime_example
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;implicit&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;none&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;real&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;::&lt;/span&gt; x, y
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;print&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;*&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#39;Enter a number:&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;read&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;*&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;*&lt;/span&gt;) x
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; y &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; sqrt(x) &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;! runtime error if x is negative
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;print&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;*&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#39;Square root:&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;, y
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;end&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;program&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;! CORRECT: Validate input before operations
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;program&lt;/span&gt; runtime_example
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;implicit&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;none&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;real&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;::&lt;/span&gt; x, y
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;print&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;*&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#39;Enter a number:&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;
